review:
This game has some weird flaws in my opinion;
The game was a little boring. Not just like, sexually boring. Usually just boring. It did this weird thing where it tried really, really hard to build this vast world with deep lore and an interesting plot... in a porn game. Now, I don't play these for the porn, so it wasn't a big deal, but the game drastically flips between someone who really cares about his world building, to a totally different person who just wants to make dirty scenes. 
Basically, it was all over the place in it's creative direction, and took a very long time for very little to happen
